    "failure_scenario": "Reviewers focused on coverage will not scrutinize a new DLQ-eligible queue handler that re-enqueues itself up to 144 times per class; a bug here (e.g. wrong attempt cap, org-circuit-breaker bypass via the `return undefined` carve-out) silently degrades real GitHub onboarding in production and is attributed to the wrong PR if it regresses."
