    "failure_scenario": "Every production student/staff repo-permission grant now has a different failure mode: a transient GitHub 'Not Found' (rate-limit masking, eventual-consistency) triggers an unexpected team CREATE on the org instead of surfacing the error, and the retry can mask genuine misconfiguration. Behavior ships unreviewed because it's hidden in a coverage diff."
